PGLookout 1.1.0
===============

* Add support for observers to participate simultaneously in multiple replication clusters, allowing observers to be shared across replication clusters
* Improved setup and install documentation
* Add Travis CI tests for Python (2.6, 2.7, 3.3 and 3.4)
* Add RPM packaging
* Add systemd support
* Compatibility fixes for Python3/PyPy
* The pglookout JSON state file has been renamed from json_state_file to pglookout_state.json
* general bug fixes


PGLookout 1.0.0
===============

* Initial release
